metadata.name: My Gift - Crystal
metadata.description:
You are a risk taker, one of the great players. You have the courage to do what others don't because you know that these experiences will reveal your great inner strength. And when the darkness presents itself, you don't turn away from your path, because in it you see the opportunity to grow.

Your life consists of actions without much thought. You trust your intuition and wisdom, knowing that God will always watch over you.

You believe that one of your biggest problems is letting your feelings take over, but that is your greatest blessing. Because your gift in life is to teach others the beauty of your inner world, without caring about anything around you.
